headline: Samsung's Google & Qualcomm VR collab, Mattel's earnings miss
summary: Yahoo Finance anchor Julie Hyman examines some of the top stories on Wall Street as part of Wednesday's Market Minute, including Mattel's (MAT) earnings miss, Capital One's (COF) share buyback, and Samsung's (005930.KS) new virtual reality (VR) headset. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
